Install Python First.
https://www.python.org/downloads/

Set your path by ticking mark or manual set in environment variable.
C:\Users\UserNAME\AppData\Local\Python\pythoncore-3.14-64\Scripts

Check you install python or not in Command prompt 
Open the Command Prompt (press Win + R, type cmd, and hit Enter) and type either of the following commands: 
python --version
python -V

